name: ratio
description:
We are driven by a ratio, 
   the golden ratio. 

Let cultures generate spaces, buildings for us to think, to enjoy art, to meet others, to discuss. 

Let the time, wars, human beings modify those spaces, those buildings, but the ratio remains there to be seen.

Let the clouds paint the sky. 

Let the computer generate the blocks with different shades. Of.

Let someone put it all together. 

Now it is yours to experience.
